commit.message:
Run tests of gcov output.

	* g77.dg/gcov: New directory.
	* g77.dg/gcov/gcov.exp: New file.
	* g77.dg/gcov/gcov-1.f: New test.
	* g77.dg/gcov/gcov-1.x: New file.

From-SVN: r45612

files.patch:
@@ -0,0 +1,44 @@

+
+# Gcov test driver.
+
+# Load support procs.
+load_lib g77-dg.exp
+load_lib gcov.exp
+
+global G77_UNDER_TEST
+
+# For now find gcov in the same directory as $G77_UNDER_TEST.
+if { ![is_remote host] && [string match "*/*" [lindex $G77_UNDER_TEST 0]] } {
+    set GCOV [file dirname [lindex $G77_UNDER_TEST 0]]/gcov
+} else {
+    set GCOV gcov
+}
+
+# Initialize harness.
+dg-init
+
+# Delete old .da files.
+set files [glob -nocomplain gcov-*.da];
+if { $files != "" } {
+    eval "remote_file build delete $files";
+}
+
+# Main loop.
+dg-runtest [lsort [glob -nocomplain $srcdir/$subdir/gcov-*.f]] "" ""
+
+dg-finish
